These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, goat, horse
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, software-developer, bartender
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, scientific
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, train, ship
1. the owner of the goat is between the musician and the person driving the skateboard##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the right of the software-developer##1
5. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the musician is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet          | snake      | goat        | horse     |
| Job         | bartender | software-developer | musician    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | musical       | scientific |
| Transport         | skateboard  | train      | ship    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, amaryllis, orchid
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, ambient, salsa
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person drinking fanta is the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the fan of soul##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
6. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person drinking fanta and the person who growsdaisy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Flower           | amaryllis    | orchid | daisy |
| Beverage   | fanta | sprite       | milk   |
| Music-Genre           | salsa  | ambient   | soul     |
| Sport         | lacrosse | tennis       | baseball   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
House: gothic-revival, art-deco, cottage
3 different games are played: canasta, bridge, go
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, light-blue, blood-red
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, train
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the cottage house is the person driving the train##1
3. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
4. the gothic-revival house is between the person playing bridge and the person driving the train##2
5. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes blood-red is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| House          | cottage | gothic-revival | art-deco |
| Game   | go     | canasta | bridge |
| Color           | light-blue       | emerald   | blood-red    |
| Transport     | train      | bike   | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard, snowmobile
City: venice, colone, rome
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, rock, salsa
There are 3 different nationalities: british, italian, pakistani
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person traveling to rome is the fan of rock##1
4. the italian is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the italian is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Transport         | skateboard  | quad-bike       | snowmobile |
| City           | rome     | colone      | venice   |
| Music-Genre   | rock | soul | salsa     |
| Nationality   | british      | pakistani   | italian     |

