.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, water
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, comedy, documentary
City: berlin, liverpool, venice
House: palace, colonial, ranch-style
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the palace house##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the ranch-style house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Beverage      | water     | juice   | coffee         |
| Movie-Genre           | action | comedy | documentary |
| City   | venice      | liverpool   | berlin            |
| House   | colonial   | ranch-style  | palace         |

