.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, video-games, magic-tricks
3 different games are played: chess, go, backgammon
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, lemonade
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, italian, mexican
1. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person playing go and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
2. the dutch is the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is the italian##1
4. the italian is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the dutch is in an even position##4
6. the dutch is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Hobby          | magic-tricks    | baking     | video-games |
| Game           | go | backgammon | chess      |
| Beverage   | lemonade      | soy-milk       | coffee    |
| Nationality   | italian      | dutch         | mexican     |

