.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, milk, cola
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, swimming, ice-hockey
House: wooden, craftsman, victorian
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, taxi
1. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
2. the craftsman house is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the wooden house is between the person driving the roller and the person drinking milk##2
7. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage          | milk | water | cola |
| Sport   | swimming  | weightlifting    | ice-hockey |
| House   | craftsman  | wooden   | victorian    |
| Transport     | taxi   | car       | roller |

