.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, rowing, biathlon
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, journalist, manager
There are 3 different nationalities: german, pakistani, russian
City: prague, hamburg, colone
1. the russian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the journalist##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the pakistani##1
6. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4
7. the videographer is between the pakistani and the person traveling to colone##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Sport      | rowing | baseball    | biathlon  |
| Job         | manager        | videographer   | journalist   |
| Nationality   | russian       | german    | pakistani |
| City     | colone          | hamburg | prague       |

