.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-9::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, july, april
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, dancer, teacher
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, turkish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, zinnia, azalea
1. the colombian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the teacher is in an even position##4
3. the turkish is the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the colombian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the lawyer##1
7. the turkish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday          | february  | july   | april      |
| Job   | dancer    | teacher      | lawyer      |
| Nationality   | canadian | colombian | turkish    |
| Flower           | azalea   | zinnia     | daffodil |

