.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-10::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts
3 different games are played: snooker, poker, billiard
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bongani, davidoff
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, van
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person playing snooker is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing snooker is the davidoff-smoker##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the van##1
6. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre           | crime     | martial-arts    | drama |
| Game   | snooker  | poker | billiard      |
| Cigar   | davidoff       | bongani   | cain    |
| Transport     | snowmobile | van        | roller     |

