.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, card-games, magic-tricks
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, hip-hop, soul
House: farmhouse, palace, cottage
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, volleyball
1. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of hip-hop is the farmhouse house##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the fan of soul is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks     | card-games      | collecting  |
| Music-Genre          | hip-hop     | soul | rock       |
| House   | farmhouse  | cottage    | palace      |
| Sport         | volleyball | badminton  | snowboarding |

