.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, cauliflower, plum
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, horror
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, begonia, amaryllis
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, july, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
2. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
7. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating pineapple and the person who growszinnia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food      | plum       | cauliflower   | pineapple |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | disaster |
| Flower           | zinnia      | begonia | amaryllis    |
| Birthday         | july  | september     | march |

