.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, hip-hop, folk
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, indian, polish
There 3 different types of food: radish, strawberry, nectarine
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
1. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
4. the polish is on the far right##1
5. the person eating radish is the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the indian is in the middle##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
8. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the indian is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre           | indie | hip-hop   | folk |
| Nationality   | argentine  | indian    | polish    |
| Food         | strawberry    | radish | nectarine   |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate  | iced-tea     | juice  |

