.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, august, september
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, reggae, punk
3 different pets are kept: snake, goat, guinea-pig
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, rowing
1. the owner of the snake is the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the fan of punk and the person who's birthday is in october##2
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Birthday         | september    | august   | october      |
| Music-Genre           | punk | d&b    | reggae |
| Pet   | snake       | goat | guinea-pig      |
| Sport         | rowing         | parkour   | climbing     |

