3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, old-henry, vegafina
1. the person who's hobby is photography is the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the chinese is in an even position##4
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the indian##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Nationality        | indian | chinese | brazilian |
| Pet         | dog       | pony    | rat       |
| Hobby       | photography  | card-games | rock-climbing      |
| Cigar   | vegafina      | bluemaster    | old-henry |

