3. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is the colonial house##1
5. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Pet          | hamster     | mouse   | bird     |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | epic   | drama      |
| House   | colonial | ranch-style | farmhouse    |
| Flower     | bellflower  | marigold   | azalea |

