.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, punk, dubstep
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, january, may
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, paramedic
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, taxi, train
1. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
2. the fan of reggae is between the fan of punk and the person driving the train##2
3. the accountant is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the designer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre          | dubstep     | reggae | punk   |
| Birthday         | may   | february | january |
| Job   | paramedic | designer       | accountant   |
| Transport     | train     | snowmobile  | taxi        |

