2. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is handball and the person eating garlic##2
3. the person drinking coffee is the palace house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person eating spinach is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2        |     3      |
| Beverage      | coffee         | sprite         | milk       |
| Food         | spinach          | orange        | garlic |
| Sport           | handball | surfing | badminton     |
| House   | palace      | gothic-revival          | victorian     |

