3. the project-manager is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the teacher is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
6. the fan of house is the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Transport          | snowmobile  | trike   | subway |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | punk      | house   |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | zombie | comedy |
