.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, lime, cranberry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, spy, superhero
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, horse, mouse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, july, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person eating lime##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
6. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Food           | mango  | cranberry | lime   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | superhero           | satire      |
| Pet           | mouse   | horse          | guinea-pig |
| Birthday     | december    | february           | july |

 